1
00:01:37,910 --> 00:01:40,990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 8]

3
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,600
Gusto lang kitang i-add sa WeChat

4
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:50,640
at tanungin kita

5
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,580
ilang mga propesyonal na katanungan.

6
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:52,150
Oo naman.

7
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:54,240
Bigyan mo muna ako ng dry cleaning fee.

8
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:55,310
Aking custom-made suit

9
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,870
nagkakahalaga ng 3,280 yuan para hugasan.

10
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,450
Bigyan mo lang ako ng 3,000 yuan.

11
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:02,200
Mr Ji, hindi mo ako masisisi sa lahat ng ito.

12
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,280
Ito ay isang aksidente.

13
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:06,000
At tingnan kung gaano sikip

14
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,120
ito ay dito.

15
00:02:10,669 --> 00:02:12,230
Siya ito.

16
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,240
Kanina lang niya ako tinulak,

17
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:16,040
at yun ang dahilan kung bakit kita nabangga.

18
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,840
Paano ba naman ako nakabangga sayo
sa sobrang layo?

19
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,560
Hindi ba't siniko mo lang ako gamit ang iyong siko

20
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,630
kaya hindi ako makatayo ng matatag

21
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:23,190
at nabangga si Mr. Ji?

22
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:30,020
naalala ko ngayon.

23
00:02:32,829 --> 00:02:36,210
Ikaw ang isa
na nanghingi sa akin ng alak ngayon lang,

24
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,680
ngunit nalaman kong champagne lang ang dala ko
sa aking tray,

25
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,280
hindi ang red wine na gusto mo,

26
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,020
kaya tumalikod ka at umalis.

27
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:46,280
Kasalanan ko lahat.

28
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,470
Champagne lang ang nasa tray ko

29
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:48,750
at hindi ang red wine na gusto mo.

30
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:51,400
Naging dahilan para tumakbo ka sa hapag kainan
napakalayo para kumuha ng alak.

31
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,770
kaya hindi sinasadyang nabangga mo si Mr.Ji.

32
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:55,490
Ito ay talagang ang aking mahinang serbisyo.

33
00:02:55,490 --> 00:02:56,280
pasensya na po.

34
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:57,310
Kalokohan!

35
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,190
Xu Miyu, naniniwala ka ba

36
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:00,910
Magsasampa ako ng reklamo laban sa iyo?

37
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:01,840
Miss,

38
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,190
pwede bang magtanong—

39
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:04,470
kumusta na siya

40
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:05,960
dapat tumulong sa iyo

41
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:07,650
magbuhos ng alak sa ginoong ito?

42
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:18,579
ganito?

43
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,030
anong nangyari?

44
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:24,910
Mr. Duan, binuhusan nila ako ng alak.

45
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:26,940
Ito ay hindi kapani-paniwalang bastos.

46
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,050
Hindi ka pa ba off work?

47
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:34,910
Sino ang gumawa nito?

48
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,120
hindi ko sinasadya!

49
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,280
Siya ito. Tinulak niya ako.

50
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,480
Sinadya niya ito.

51
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:39,840
Miss,

52
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,560
mangyaring magsalita ng lohikal, okay?

53
00:03:42,579 --> 00:03:44,579
Ano ang mapapala niya sa pag-set up sa iyo?

54
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,680
Papakasalan mo ba siya,

55
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,280
o suportahan siya o ano?

56
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:49,930
kilala ba kita

57
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,160
Sumama ako kay Vivian.

58
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,560
Sino si Vivian?

59
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,000
Hakbang pasulong!

60
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:02,360
Sorry, walang Vivian dito.

61
00:04:03,210 --> 00:04:04,800
Kailangan kong makita ang iyong imbitasyon.

62
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,080
Nakalusot ka ba?

63
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,730
Hindi.

64
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,130
Hahanapin ko para sayo.

65
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,240
saan ito?

66
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,390
Seryoso,

67
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,240
pwede bang itigil mo na ang mga taong ganito

68
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,480
pumasok ka at sirain ang kaganapan ko?

69
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,270
Paumanhin, Mr. Duan.

70
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,530
Hindi na mauulit.

71
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,270
Ayos lang, maglaro ka.

72
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:26,840
ayos lang.

73
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,680
Sige na.

74
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:28,430
Halika na.

75
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:29,520
Ituloy natin.

76
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,850
pasensya na po.

77
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,800
Sa tuwing may party,

78
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,800
laging may mga tao
ganito ang papasok.

79
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,240
Tanggalin mo ang iyong suit

80
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,270
at tatanungin ko ang hotel
upang hawakan ito para sa iyo.

81
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:37,870
Kalimutan mo na.

82
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,610
Iyong laundry room
malamang hindi kakayanin.

83
00:04:39,610 --> 00:04:40,950
Ako mismo ang mag-iisip.

84
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:41,770
Mr. Ji,

85
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,680
hayaan mo akong kunin ang suit.

86
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:46,430
May kilala akong dry cleaner sa South Maoming Road

87
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:48,000
na dalubhasa sa mga high-end na suit.

88
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,950
Ginagawa nila ang isang mahusay na trabaho.

89
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:50,270
Dadalhin ko na agad.

90
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,330
Hindi masyadong pipi.

91
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,430
Pumunta ka dali.

92
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,600
Magkaroon ng HSKP Department

93
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,560
takpan ang pera sa ngayon—

94
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,890
singilin ito sa aking account.

95
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,430
Pagkatapos mangyaring hawakan ito para sa akin.

96
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,159
salamat po.

97
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,830
Ang HSKP Department ay may magandang lasa.

98
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,900
Siya ay medyo matalino.

99
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,160
At mayroon siyang

100
00:05:15,010 --> 00:05:16,010
sarili niyang alindog din.

101
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,600
Taga executive floor ba siya?

102
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,290
Paano naman yung babaeng chef na yun?

103
00:05:24,290 --> 00:05:25,550
Tumakas na naman ba siya?

104
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:28,390
Miyu.

105
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,630
bakit ka nandito?

106
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,610
Ano bang nangyayari sayo?

107
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,240
Hindi ka nakapasa sa internal referral
huling pagkakataon.

108
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,000
Diba sabi mo maghahanap ka ng ibang trabaho?

109
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,360
Paano mo nagawa ito?

110
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,560
At hindi mo man lang sinabi sa akin.

111
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,760
Hindi na ganoon kadaling maghanap ng trabaho sa panahon ngayon.

112
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:45,240
Isa akong maybahay sa edad na thirties

113
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:46,659
na may blangkong resume.

114
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,390
Walang may gusto sa akin kahit saan.

115
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:50,790
Ngunit hindi mo dapat kailanganin
magtrabaho bilang isang tagapaglinis.

116
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,800
Sabihin mo sa akin ang totoo,

117
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,680
may problema ka ba?

118
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,600
Hindi.

119
00:05:56,050 --> 00:05:56,870
Walang nagpilit sa akin.

120
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,000
Ako mismo ang pumili nito.

121
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,270
Hindi ako nagtrabaho nang napakaraming taon,

122
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:02,240
Kailangan kong magsimula sa ibaba.

123
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,720
Huwag kang mag-alala, Qiaoqi.

124
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,390
ayos lang ako.

125
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:06,240
Sinabi ko sa iyo na ako ang iyong hagdan.

126
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:07,120
Nakatalikod ako sayo.

127
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,800
Okay, nasa likod mo ako.

128
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,930
tatandaan ko yan.

129
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,040
Bumalik ka na sa trabaho.

130
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,240
Kailangan ko ding maging abala.

131
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,720
Mag-usap tayo mamaya.

132
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,040
Ate, tinakot mo ako hanggang sa mamatay.

133
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,100
anong ginagawa mo

134
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,040
Ni-recruit mo ba si Xu Miyu

135
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:34,990
sa executive floor?

136
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:36,560
WHO?

137
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,159
Xu Miyu!

138
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,720
Xu Mi...

139
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:45,480
Hindi ka ba humingi sa akin ng pabor
sa panahon ng panayam?

140
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,000
Hindi pumasa ang resume niya.

141
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,560
Pero pag nakikita ko siyang ganyan,

142
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,710
Binigyan ko siya ng suggestion.

143
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,620
Kaya tinanong ko siya

144
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:54,360
kung gusto niyang subukan
simula bilang isang katulong.

145
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,060
Dumating talaga siya.

146
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,240
Hindi,

147
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,800
Hiniling kong tulungan mo siya

148
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,800
mag-apply para sa Marketing Department,

149
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,720
at pinadala mo siya para maging isang katulong.

150
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,360
Kuya,

151
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,040
I treat you like a brother,

152
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,570
at tinatrato mo ako na parang tanga?

153
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,240
Sis,

154
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,720
Sumusumpa ako sa Diyos,

155
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,390
Hindi ako mangangahas na tratuhin ka na parang tanga.

156
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:12,920
Parang sabik na sabik siya,

157
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,600
at hindi siya makapasok
ang Marketing Department anumang oras sa lalong madaling panahon,

158
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,130
kaya nag-isip ako ng paraan para sa kanya.

159
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,720
Sa tingin mo ba ay nagkaroon siya ng problema

160
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,180
at nangangailangan ng pera nang madalian?

161
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,820
May sinabi ba siya sayo?

162
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,040
Hello. Ano ang huling apat na digit
ng iyong numero ng telepono?

163
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,300
Ano ang huling apat na digit?

164
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:41,270
6453.

165
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,360
Anong uri ng lihim na code ito?

166
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,120
Sir,

167
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,720
huwag kang magalit.

168
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,600
Ito ay hindi isang lihim na code.

169
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,920
Isa itong ride-hailing app.

170
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,800
Ride-hailing?

171
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,480
Uber?

172
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,159
Oo.

173
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,590
Ito ay katulad sa Uber.

174
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,600
Kailangan mo lang ipasok ang iyong patutunguhan

175
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,890
sa address bar.

176
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,500
Sobrang gulo.

177
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,600
Dati, pumara ka lang ng taksi

178
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,870
at umalis ka.

179
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,480
Actually, hindi naman ganoon kahirap.

180
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,010
Paano kung ipasok ko ito para sa iyo?

181
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,480
Excuse me, Miss...

182
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,480
Ako ay mula sa HSKP Department
ng Purong Hotel.

183
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,480
Ang pangalan ko ay Xu Miyu.

184
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:15,920
Sige.

185
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,000
Pagkatapos,

186
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,800
salamat sa problema mo.

187
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,930
Saan mo gustong pumunta?

188
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:23,800
No. 18 Qinfang Garden, Aiguo Road.

189
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,390
Okay.

190
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,630
[Pickup: Purong Hotel]
[Destinasyon: Qinfang Garden, Aiguo Road]

191
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,830
Dito ba?

192
00:08:28,970 --> 00:08:29,360
Okay.

193
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,600
Nakapasok na.

194
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,360
Mangyaring maghintay ng ilang sandali.

195
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,610
Malapit nang dumating ang sasakyan.

196
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:33,470
yun lang?

197
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,289
Ito dapat ang kotse.

198
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,840
Ito ay mahusay.

199
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,080
salamat po.

200
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:42,600
Bahala ka,

201
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,210
Ms. Xu.

202
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:43,840
Hindi, hindi.

203
00:08:44,179 --> 00:08:44,670
Kunin mo.

204
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,150
Hindi ko talaga matatanggap ito.

205
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:46,750
salamat po.

206
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,280
Sige na.

207
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:52,000
maraming salamat.

208
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:55,480
Paalam.

209
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:03,550
Alam kong hindi ako nagkamali sayo,

210
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:04,270
Xu Miyu.

211
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:05,590
Direktor Xue.

212
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,840
Balita ko na-assign ka sa
ang executive floor.

213
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,360
paano ito?

214
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,820
Nasanay ka na ba sa bagong trabaho?

215
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:12,360
Maraming bagay na dapat matutunan,

216
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,030
ngunit sinusubukan ko ang aking makakaya.

217
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:17,720
Laging may hirap
sa simula.

218
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,360
Magiging maayos kapag nalampasan mo ito.

219
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,240
Ikaw ay isang tao
na may propesyonal na hangarin.

220
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:22,900
Maniwala ka sa akin,

221
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,600
lalo kang gagaling,

222
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,790
at pumunta sa susunod na antas.

223
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,390
salamat po.

224
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:27,750
Ituloy mo yan.

225
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,080
Room service.

226
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:40,310
Hello, Mr. Ji.

227
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,090
Nalabhan na ang iyong mga damit.

228
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:43,420
salamat po.

229
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:46,550
Ayaw mo bang suriin

230
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,550
kung ito ay malinis

231
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,030
o kung may nasira?

232
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,390
ayos lang. Salamat

233
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:54,790
para pumunta dito.

234
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:55,590
Sandali lang.

235
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:00,830
Naaalala mo ba ang

236
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,460
magandang review na bagay
napag usapan natin last time?

237
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:04,600
Oo.

238
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,390
So would this meet

239
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:11,670
ang iyong mga pamantayan para sa isang mahusay na pagsusuri?

240
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,240
Humihingi ka ba ng magandang review sa mga bisita

241
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,480
araw-araw sa trabaho?

242
00:10:14,770 --> 00:10:15,320
Hindi.

243
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,440
Wala akong natanong sa iba.

244
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,490
Kaya lalo akong pinarangalan?

245
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,360
Bakit gusto mo ang magandang review ko?

246
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,220
Dahil ikaw...

247
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,840
Dahil ikaw
ang aming iginagalang na Black Card VIP.

248
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:27,840
Kaya?

249
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,360
Naglinis na ako ng kwarto
eksakto sa tinanong mo,

250
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,120
mabilis at maayos,

251
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,120
at hindi naman kita inistorbo diba?

252
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,440
natanggap ko na
dalawang masamang review ngayong buwan.

253
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,000
Kung makakuha ako ng isa pa,

254
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,840
buong bonus ko
para ang buwan ay mawawala.

