00:34:28,510 --> 00:34:29,670
Xu Miyu?

761
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:31,230
Sino siya?

762
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:32,880
Isang baguhan.

763
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:35,590
Isang baguhan,

764
00:34:35,590 --> 00:34:36,510
at hindi mo siya kayang hawakan?

765
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:37,320
Hindi.

766
00:34:37,710 --> 00:34:38,630
Nakita ko...

767
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,760
Nakita ko siyang kumuha ng bote ng shampoo

768
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:43,260
mula sa isang guest room sa nakakalito na paraan.

769
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,760
Hindi ko alam kung anong ginagawa niya.

770
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,090
At hindi ako naglakas loob na magtanong.

771
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:47,000
Nag-aalala ako

772
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:49,280
baka may nalaman siya.

773
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,010
Zhang Cailu,

774
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:51,090
hayaan mong sabihin ko sa iyo,

775
00:34:51,150 --> 00:34:52,860
ayusin ang mga bagay.

776
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:53,710
Ikaw ba ang forewoman,

777
00:34:53,710 --> 00:34:54,400
o siya ba?

778
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:56,400
Hindi mo mapamahalaan

779
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:57,330
bagong katulong?

780
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,510
Gusto mo pa bang kunin ang iyong anak na babae

781
00:34:58,510 --> 00:34:59,960
sa Maldives para sa Bisperas ng Bagong Taon?

782
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,580
Oo, siyempre ginagawa ko.

783
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:05,000
Pero araw-araw akong nababaliw.

784
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:07,630
Napakalaki ng pressure.

785
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:09,000
Hindi kaya ng katawan ko.

786
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:12,000
Bakit hindi mo sinabi yan

787
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,330
nung kinuha mo yung pera?

788
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,550
Gusto mo lang kumita

789
00:35:14,550 --> 00:35:15,880
nang hindi inaako ang responsibilidad.

790
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,710
Kung hindi talaga kaya ng katawan mo,
itigil ang paggawa nito.

791
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:19,840
Maraming tao ang gusto.

792
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:21,150
Hindi, hindi.

793
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:23,360
Wala akong ibig sabihin niyan.

794
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,220
Ibig kong sabihin,

795
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:25,230
Talagang hindi ako papayag

796
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,560
na Xu Miyu off.

797
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:28,070
Sa loob ng ilang araw, hahanap ako ng random na dahilan

798
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:29,110
para tanggalin siya.

799
00:35:29,590 --> 00:35:31,510
Siguradong hindi kita guguluhin.

800
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:33,070
Wala akong pakialam kung paano mo ito ginagawa.

801
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:34,590
Gawin itong maganda.

802
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:35,800
Huwag mong ipagpaliban ang mga plano ko!

803
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:36,400
Okay.

804
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:37,350
Panigurado.

805
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:01,760
Miyu.

806
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,860
Um...

807
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,630
Ikaw ba ay

808
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,290
