maging nostalhik sa bahay?

865
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:11,800
Senior, para kang food map.

866
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:14,070
Sayang ang kasama mo
Kagawaran ng Pananalapi.

867
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,550
Dapat kang pumunta sa Marketing Department

868
